  <h2 style="text-align:center; color:#2a3eb1;">Why Use This Study Planner?</h2>
  <p>This Study Planner & Time Management Tool is designed to help students of all levels—middle school, high school, and college—organize their homework, assignments, and study sessions efficiently. By visualizing tasks, estimated completion times, and breaks, students can manage their workload without feeling overwhelmed.</p>
 
  <p>The tool uses the <strong>Most Important Task (MIT) Method</strong> to prioritize the most challenging assignments first, helping students make the most of their attention span. It also incorporates strategic 15-minute breaks, proven to improve memory retention and reduce cognitive fatigue, allowing students to study smarter, not longer.</p>
 
  <p>With this planner, students can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Track assignments and homework by subject and difficulty level</li>
    <li>Visualize a multi-day schedule to balance work and rest</li>
    <li>Boost productivity with scientifically-backed breaks</li>
    <li>Manage time effectively and reduce last-minute stress</li>
  </ul>
 
  <p>Whether you want to plan your entire week of homework or just focus on a single study session, this tool helps students take control of their time and improve academic performance. Using it consistently can lead to better time management, higher productivity, and more free time for extracurricular activities.</p>
 
